            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Saporellus">Saporello</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Nerlus">Nirllo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> et alio
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes/Pappulino">Iohannes que
                                Pappulino</name></persName> vocatur germani filii bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Morranus/Corpulus">Morrani que
                            Corpulo</name></persName> vocatur ricevono in livello da <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/219">Stefano</persName> in Christi nomine <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/126">Sancti
                            Bartholomei</orgName> sito loco <placeName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#places/281">Sextinghe</placeName> (…) una <rs key="#Petiae"
                            >petia</rs> de terra illa, quod est <rs key="#Cereals">terra
                            laboratoria</rs> et <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs> insimul compreensa (…)
                        quod esse videtur in loco et finibus <placeName
                            key="#Petiae #Size #Cereals #Wine" ref="#places/274">Morrano et
                            vocitatur a Perita</placeName>, tenentes uno capo in terra et vinea quod
                        fui quondam <persName key="#Confinia #Petiae #Wine"><name
                                ref="Ilditius dal Prato">Ilditii dal Prato</name></persName> et alio
                        capo tene in terra <persName key="#Confinia #Petiae"><name ref="Rotius"
                                >Roctii</name></persName> et <persName key="#Confinia #Petiae"><name
                                ref="Sclavus">Sclavi</name></persName> germani, lato uno tene in
                        terra <orgName key="#Confinia #Petiae" ref="#juridical_persons/124">Sancti
                            Laurentii</orgName>, alio lato tene in terra <orgName
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae" ref="#juridical_persons/124">Sancti Laurentii
                        </orgName>et alliquantulo in terra de fili quondam <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Specialized_workers"><name ref="Gherardinus"
                                >Ghirardini</name></persName> qui fui <rs key="#Specialized_workers"
                            >aurifex</rs>, con tutte le sue dipendenze qua sunt <rs key="#Size">tres
                            tramiti</rs> in integrum. Si impegnano a versare pro omni censum et
                        iustitiam all’abate e ai suoi successori ogni mese di agosto al monastero il
                        censo annuale di argentu denariis boni expendibilibus numeros tres, nam post
                        ipsa pensione data et ostensa abuerimus tu qui supra Stefano abbas vel
                        tuique successores aut vestro misso ipsa pensione da nobis in <rs
                            key="#Beneficium">beneficio</rs> perdere et dare debeatis. Se non
                        rispetteranno i suddetti impegni, promettono con i loro eredi di versare
                        all’abate e ai suoi successori la pena di 20 soldi d’argento. Chiedono a
                            <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Rodelandus"
                            >Rodilandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domini imperatoris la stesura di due
                        cartulas. Actu in loco <placeName key="#Baptismal_churches"
                            ref="#places/274">Morrano</placeName> prope <rs
                            key="#Baptismal_churches">eccclesia e plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/125">Sancti
                            Donati</orgName>. Sottoscrivono: Saporelli et Nirlli et Iohannis et alio
                        Iohanni qui Pappulino vocatur germani. Testi: <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Gherardus">Gherardi</name></persName> filio bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Rusticus">Rustichi</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rodelandus">Rollandi</name></persName> filio
                        bone memorie <persName><name ref="Albo">Alboni</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Lambertus">Lamberti</name></persName> filio
                        bone memorie <persName><name ref="Hubertus">Uberti</name></persName>.
                        Scrive: Rodilandus notarius domni imperatoris. </ab>
                        </div>
